{"tid":2424542,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【理大圍城】被控理大暴動 應屆文憑試女生申保釋再度被拒 上庭時一臉憔悴","createTime":"2021-02-26T15:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T01:32:35.000Z","uid":240362,"like":11,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"1c4be0dc7941ce7e46fe57a1114c527c76b75fc0","tid":2424542,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T15:46:20.000Z","msg":"（獨媒報導）前年11月警方圍堵理大校園，其中12人被捕後踢保，惟事隔一年多後，上周再被捕即日火速被帶上庭，全被控理大一帶參與暴動等罪。主任裁判官嚴舜儀拒絕11人保釋，包括一名17歲應屆文憑試中六女生。她今（26日）在九龍城法院申請保釋覆核，她上庭時一臉憔悴，最後遭裁判官鄭念慈拒絕保釋。據悉，下月為其學校的最後上課日子，而4月將是文憑試開考。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1081092\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1081092&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2BzC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=fca894e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1081092&h=365d9ac5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1081092</a>"},{"pid":"041c2ec24b281ed8bf319eff71b636ea8bda7593","tid":2424542,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T15:46:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9856fdedb1e991ff549ffc8fdc217f7f97f975","tid":2424542,"uid":280525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T15:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8eda24fea4686d951edda7952c15bdfecb7a20b","tid":2424542,"uid":184261,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T15:47:00.000Z","msg":"吃子政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor